 {
  "text": "Hi, my name is Sara. I am a nurse at the clinic. Today is very busy. Many patients have a fever. One patient has a cough and a stomach ache. Another patient has a sore arm. The last patient has a sore throat and a cough. It is a long day, but I like my job. I help people every day.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a15_listening_a_day_at_the_clinic.mp3"
 },
 {
